  "body": "The pod eviction subresource should trust PDBs only when they are synced by the PDB controller (pdb.generation == pdb.status.observedGeneration) instead of relying unconditionally on [PodDisruptionAllowed](https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/6bda989d5497f47f4454a7fc81eaea877f404861/pkg/registry/core/pod/etcd/eviction.go#L106) (or the new integer field that will replace PodDisruptionAllowed). /evict should probably set a RetryAfter header or poll for some time the pdb. \n\n@mml @mwielgus @davidopp \n",
